1
00:01:57,039 --> 00:02:00,440
Your Majesty, an epidemic
has broken out in Huangpi Village.

2
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,490
Dozens of people are infected.

3
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,510
The situation

4
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,430
doesn't look good.

5
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,800
Open the door.

6
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,150
How could you just leave us,

7
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,750
abandoning me and your child?

8
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,079
Make way.

9
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,860
Careful, make way.

10
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:38,910
Fei Zheng,

11
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,850
what do you think we should do?

12
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:41,960
Your Majesty,

13
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,030
I believe

14
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:45,680
we should send physicians
to Huangpi Village,

15
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,000
set up quarantine areas,

16
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:49,130
to prevent the spread of the epidemic.

17
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:51,079
Meanwhile, we should
allocate food and medicine

18
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:52,810
to meet the needs of the people.

19
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:54,190
If necessary,

20
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,590
we can ask the Eldest Princess

21
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:57,560
to allocate funds from the treasury

22
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,870
to support Huangpi Village
with all available resources.

23
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:00,520
Good.

24
00:03:00,710 --> 00:03:01,520
Let's do it.

25
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,600
Your Majesty,

26
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:05,630
Lord Fei makes it sound easy,

27
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:08,470
but it won't be so simple in practice.

28
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,680
Lord Fei said

29
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,840
to send physicians
to Huangpi Village.

30
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,680
If they get infected,

31
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:15,470
who will treat them?

32
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,150
He also said

33
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,750
to set up quarantine areas.

34
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:20,870
If all infected people go there,

35
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:23,400
who will take care of their daily needs?

36
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,360
Are we leaving them to die?

37
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,870
We need to transport food and medicine.

38
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:29,870
If infection occurs during transport,

39
00:03:29,870 --> 00:03:33,190
wouldn't it harm more innocent people?

40
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,190
Furthermore,

41
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,840
are the treasury funds

42
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,030
meant for commoners to use?

43
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,630
Lord Li makes sense.

44
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,680
If the physicians get sick,

45
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,840
it will indeed be troublesome.

46
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,590
Yes.

47
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,870
If the disease spreads to the capital,

48
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,520
the consequences will be unimaginable.

49
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,590
Lord Fei

50
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:49,280
is still too young.

51
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:51,090
You all are absolutely right.

52
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,470
I'm sure Lord Li has a brilliant idea.

53
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,960
Why not speak up

54
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,470
and enlighten us

55
00:03:57,470 --> 00:03:58,800
so we may learn from you?

56
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,280
Your Majesty,

57
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,800
the epidemic is spreading.

58
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,590
If we don't take decisive measures

59
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,360
and allow it to worsen,

60
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,840
not only the capital

61
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,630
but all of Jinglan

62
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:15,280
will fall into an abyss of no return.

63
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,480
Lord Zhang,

64
00:04:17,269 --> 00:04:18,560
what kind of

65
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:20,510
decisive measures

66
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,060
are you talking about?

67
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,280
Your Majesty,

68
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,430
to save the people of Jinglan,

69
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,830
we must act decisively.

70
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:31,560
If necessary, we must
abandon Huangpi Village.

71
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,280
Your Majesty,

72
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:38,690
I believe this method
is absolutely unacceptable.

73
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,870
The people are innocent.

74
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:41,750
We should do our best to treat them.

75
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,150
We cannot give up easily.

76
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,159
Xiao Chi.

77
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:47,560
You have killed so many
enemies on the battlefield.

78
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,870
Why are you

79
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:50,800
being soft-hearted at this time?

80
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,120
The ones I killed on the battlefield

81
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
were enemies.

82
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:54,870
And those you are going to abandon

83
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,560
are the people of Jinglan.

84
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:59,560
It is for the sake of more people

85
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:02,270
that I abandon a small Huangpi Village.

86
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,430
We,

87
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:04,830
all of us here,

88
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:08,600
are people who have experienced
the disaster 8 years ago.

89
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,630
At that time,

90
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:12,240
it was because we were soft-hearted

91
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,430
that the people of the whole Jinglan

92
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,190
suffered terribly.

93
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,480
At that time,

94
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,680
you and Lord Fei were still young.

95
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:23,070
His Majesty was also young.

96
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,560
It's understandable that you forget

97
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,830
about this matter quickly.

98
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:29,000
Lord Zhang.

99
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,160
We were ignorant at that time.

100
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:31,950
Now,

101
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,440
we can definitely solve this epidemic.

102
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,480
Okay.

103
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,680
Then General Xiao,

104
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:41,600
you will be personally
responsible for this.

105
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,000
Do you dare to go?

106
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,120
Of course.

107
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:47,870
Your Majesty,

108
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,040
I am willing to go with General Xiao.

109
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:51,560
Xiao Chi.

110
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:52,950
The epidemic in Huangpi Village

111
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,070
is serious.

112
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:55,830
Are you

113
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,630
really going?

114
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,240
Your Majesty,

115
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,270
human effort can achieve anything.

116
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:03,510
I will definitely not let
the tragedy of 8 years ago

117
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,480
happen again.

118
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:05,750
Fei Zheng,

119
00:06:06,630 --> 00:06:08,160
stay by my side

120
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,830
and be on standby.

121
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,000
Xiao Chi.

122
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:13,950
You must be very careful

123
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,160
this time when you go

124
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,540
to Huangpi Village

125
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,360
to save the people.

126
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,160
Yes.

127
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,520
It's fine if the disease
can be controlled.

128
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,070
If it can't be controlled...

129
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,680
Lord Zhang,

130
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:30,560
what do you think?

131
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,760
Your Majesty has already decided.

132
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:33,830
I

133
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,659
have no objection.

134
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:36,950
Alright.

135
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,730
Xiao Chi, receive the decree.

136
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,070
I obey.

137
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,600
If you go to Huangbei Village

138
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,830
to aid the people

139
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,270
and return victorious,

140
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:51,240
I shall elevate you
as a pillar of the state.

141
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,370
I accept the decree,

142
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,360
and will definitely
not fail Your Majesty's trust

143
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,159
and the people's expectations.

144
00:06:58,950 --> 00:06:59,800
Xiao Chi?

145
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:01,560
You're awake.

146
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,190
You were

147
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:05,750
asleep just now,

148
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:07,550
so I didn't go in and disturb you.

149
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,240
You're looking for me
about Huangpi Village, right?

150
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,040
That's right.

151
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:13,160
The situation in Huangpi Village
is very serious this time.

152
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,680
So I cannot stay out of it.

153
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,430
I know.

154
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,430
But if you get infected,

155
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:17,830
you...

156
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,410
Everyone will worry about you.

157
00:07:27,830 --> 00:07:29,030
I know what I'm doing.

158
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,240
Healing the sick is my bounden duty.

159
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:33,680
I can't back down just because
I'm afraid of getting infected.

160
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,390
I have never doubted your medical skills.

161
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:37,000
But this time is truly different.

162
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,430
If I don't go,

163
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,360
do you have a better candidate?

164
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:52,360
We'll face this together.

165
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,070
Alright.

166
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,480
But promise me,

167
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,330
you must not act on your own.

168
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,000
When it comes to treating the illness,

169
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,870
I am in charge,

170
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,680
and you must cooperate with me.

171
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:04,630
Alright,

172
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,270
I will cooperate.

173
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:08,560
By the grace of Heaven,

174
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,070
the Emperor proclaims:

175
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:11,810
An epidemic has broken out
in Huangpi Village,

176
00:08:11,810 --> 00:08:13,560
and the people are in danger.

177
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:16,390
I heard Physician Han
is well-versed in pharmacology.

178
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:19,870
The Imperial Medical Academy
is ordered to follow her command,

179
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:22,630
and assist in the dispatch
of all medical supplies.

180
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:24,160
Make no mistake.

181
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:24,950
So ordered.

182
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:25,680
Let me test you.

183
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,750
What is this?

184
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:27,870
This is Angelica.

185
00:08:27,870 --> 00:08:28,630
Mmm.

186
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:29,600
Yunling.

187
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:31,360
Even though you are a girl,

188
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,030
I want you to become

189
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:35,750
a physician who can
treat the common people,

190
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:38,480
with a benevolent heart and skilled hands.

191
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:41,320
I will definitely not
let you down, Father.

192
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,480
Mmm.

193
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,240
Mo.

194
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,880
Your injuries have healed a lot.

195
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:27,680
It seems Liu Xiyang
has taken good care of you.

196
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,870
Tomorrow,

197
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:33,030
I have to go out with Xiao Chi

198
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,960
to handle some important matters.

199
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:38,500
I won't be able to visit you
for the next few days.

200
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,080
Mo.

201
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,240
Wake up soon.

202
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:53,240
If Uncle Lie knew you were still alive,

203
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:55,200
how happy he would be!

204
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,080
As long as I come back safely,

205
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:04,160
I will definitely save you
and bring you back.

206
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:15,080
The medicines and necessities
have been loaded onto the carts.

207
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,360
Good. Thank you.

208
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:21,200
General Xiao.

209
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:27,870
Lord Zhang.

210
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,030
General Xiao.

211
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:37,030
You're about to leave for Huangpi Village.

212
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:37,960
I have

213
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:40,630
specially prepared a gift for you.

214
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,630
A gift?

215
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,600
This is a token of my regard.

216
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,200
I wish you a speedy victory,

217
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,670
a safe return,

218
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:54,750
and promotion with wealth.

219
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,240
I accept your

220
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,600
kind intentions.

221
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,120
I won't

222
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:01,550
fail to live up to your expectations.

223
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,870
That's good.

224
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:04,790
I hope the two of you

225
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,480
look out for yourselves.

226
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,090
I won't see you out.

227
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,480
Humph.

228
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,330
You can put up with that?

229
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,160
It's nothing.

230
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,550
At Tianlang Pass,

231
00:11:17,750 --> 00:11:19,150
I've seen plenty of this.

232
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,630
Xiao Chi.

233
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,480
The epidemic in Huangpi Village

234
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,390
is no joke.

235
00:11:25,270 --> 00:11:25,870
You two must

236
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:27,870
prioritize your own safety
above everything else.

237
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,200
Don't push yourselves.

238
00:11:29,550 --> 00:11:30,750
Rest assured, Zheng.

239
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,030
Let's go.

240
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:32,600
Okay.

241
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:57,960
I didn't expect

242
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,150
it to be so serious.

243
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:01,600
Sir!

244
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,720
Sir!

245
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,670
Please open the door!

246
00:12:03,670 --> 00:12:05,000
Save my child!

247
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,480
Sir!

248
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,670
Save my child!

249
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,390
Open it.

250
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,030
Save my child!

251
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:14,390
Sir, please save my child!

252
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:16,030
He's dying.

253
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,240
He's dying!

254
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,840
The child is already dead.

255
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,480
No!

256
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,030
This isn't real.

257
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:24,960
My condolences.

258
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,440
You're lying to me.

259
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,360
Are you okay?

260
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,670
You're lying to me!

261
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:38,670
Let's go in and check on the others first.

262
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:39,440
After going in,

263
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,000
make sure to protect yourself.

264
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,240
My child!

265
00:12:53,030 --> 00:12:54,390
Has the court just given up on us?

266
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:56,150
Are they leaving us to die?

267
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:56,750
Yeah! Yeah!

268
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:57,670
We are just...

269
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,270
Just what?

270
00:12:59,270 --> 00:12:59,910
We're just nobodies

271
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:01,390
from a small place like Huangpi Village.

272
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,480
If we die,

273
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,240
who will care?

274
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,120
Who will care?

275
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,000
Right!

276
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,000
Don't worry, everyone.

277
00:13:07,390 --> 00:13:08,080
His Majesty

278
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,860
will not abandon any subject of Jinglan.

279
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:13,080
General Xiao, you're finally here.

280
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,240
This is General Xiao.

281
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:16,150
Folks, we are saved!

282
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,870
Don't worry, everyone.

283
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,390
We will do our best

284
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,960
to help everyone get out of danger.

285
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,760
General Xiao,

286
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,630
I believe in you.

287
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:23,630
We believe in you.

288
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:25,630
We believe in you!

289
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:27,080
We believe in you!

290
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,870
Everyone, come and get your medicine.

291
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:31,630
Please cooperate with
the physicians' treatment,

292
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:32,750
to contain the disease
as soon as possible.

293
00:13:32,750 --> 00:13:34,080
Line up!

294
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:35,240
Great!

295
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,870
Line up!

296
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,550
Thank you, Sir.

297
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,360
Thank you.

298
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,010
General.

299
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,200
I am Chen Yuan,

300
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,670
the physician
in charge of Huangpi Village.

301
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:47,550
This is...

302
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:48,640
Han Yunling,

303
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,200
a physician who came
with me from the border.

304
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:53,200
Tell her about the current situation.

305
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:53,840
Yes.

306
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,270
In the past few days,

307
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,480
I've gone through the medical texts,

308
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,790
and found that these symptoms

309
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,790
closely resemble the Death Plague.

310
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,030
But for the so-called Death Plague,

311
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:03,480
there are no recorded cases
of successful treatment.

312
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,480
I really

313
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,360
have no idea what to do.

314
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:07,750
According to the records

315
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:09,600
in Uncle Lie's notes, Death Plague

316
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,000
is transmissible among humans.

317
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,360
We should find a clean place

318
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,600
to serve as a specialized
treatment facility,

319
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:15,840
and treat all
the infected patients in isolation

320
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,630
to prevent future trouble.

321
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:17,750
Is there a cure?

322
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,870
Although there are
ancient prescriptions in the notes,

323
00:14:19,870 --> 00:14:21,030
whether they are feasible

324
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,090
remains to be seen.

325
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,480
In that case,

326
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:24,840
separate the patients

327
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,870
from the others

328
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:26,670
and treat them in isolation.

329
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:28,270
Everyone inside is sick.

330
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:30,480
Won't we get infected if we go in?

331
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,240
Exactly. No way.

332
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,440
My family has had only
1 son for 3 generations.

333
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,870
Whoever wants to go can go.

334
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:36,840
I know you are all afraid,

335
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,670
but they are our family.

336
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,670
They need us the most right now.

337
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:42,030
Please rest assured,

338
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:43,320
I will go in with you.

339
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,080
Who are you?

340
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,440
Why should I trust you?

341
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,360
Exactly.

342
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,030
A little girl

343
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,750
pretending to be a military doctor.

344
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,810
Listen, everyone.

345
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,030
Isn't this little girl
just messing around?

346
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:52,790
Right.

347
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,790
Exactly.

348
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,670
Physician Han was sent by His Majesty.

349
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:56,930
If you don't trust her,

350
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,480
do you not trust His Majesty?

351
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,390
General Xiao.

352
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:01,000
Can this little girl

353
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,000
really cure that darn Death Plague?

354
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,200
Although Death Plague is dangerous,

355
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,720
it's not incurable.

356
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:07,480
Physician Han

357
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,410
will do her best to treat everyone.

358
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,680
Please rest assured.

359
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,030
Physician Han.

360
00:15:15,030 --> 00:15:17,960
My sister and I want to
help at the quarantine center.

361
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,750
Sure.

362
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,840
But what about the adults
from your family?

363
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,150
We don't have any.

364
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,240
They are sisters.

365
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,270
The older one is Cuizhi,

366
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,750
and the younger one is Cuimiao.

367
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,790
Their parents

368
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:30,030
also got Death Plague

369
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:32,320
and died the day before yesterday.

370
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,200
Then both of you come and help,

371
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:36,840
okay?

372
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:38,870
Okay.

373
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,550
General Xiao has fought for years
to defend the country.

374
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,960
I trust you. I'll go.

375
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:44,080
I'll go too.

376
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,240
We'll go too.

377
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,970
You must be careful.

378
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,870
The medicine is here.

379
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:54,550
The water is here.

380
00:15:54,550 --> 00:15:56,150
Quick, bring the medicine.

381
00:15:56,150 --> 00:15:56,630
Over here.

382
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:59,840
Coming.

383
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,670
Careful, it's hot.

384
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:01,240
Go get some water.

385
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,080
Bring another basin of water.

386
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,670
Someone is coughing up blood inside again.

387
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:06,870
Coming.

388
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:09,750
How is it?

389
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,280
Everything is fine for now.

390
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,840
Physician Han, this patient is dying.

391
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,610
Please go and check on him.

392
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,200
Come and check on him.

393
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,790
Go get Physician Han.

394
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:36,630
Physician Han.

395
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:37,550
This patient is dying.

396
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,840
Come and check on him.

397
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,840
Let me see.

398
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,829
I am willing to sacrifice my life

399
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,740
to end this disaster in Huangpi Village.

400
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,349
Thank you.

401
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:31,640
Thank you, Sir.

402
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,240
Thank you.

403
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,240
Thank you.

404
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:40,400
How is the situation with Xiao Chi?

405
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,680
There is no news yet.

406
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:44,550
So many days have passed.

407
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:47,590
Why is there no news at all?

408
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,960
Your Majesty,

409
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:51,030
I came to see you today

410
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:53,630
to ask for permission
to go to Huangpi Village.

411
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,480
Okay.

412
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,000
Then,

413
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,160
take care.

414
00:18:03,030 --> 00:18:04,550
Don't go empty-handed.

415
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,160
Xie, why are you here?

416
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,260
Your Highness.

417
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:10,750
As the Eldest Princess,

418
00:18:10,750 --> 00:18:11,680
how could I stand by and do nothing

419
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,680
with the situation in Huangpi Village?

420
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:16,540
I have ordered people
to prepare food and medicine,

421
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,040
as well as Atractylodes.

422
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:20,590
I heard that burning Atractylodes
can ward off the plague.

423
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:22,160
I hope it can help them.

424
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:24,020
Xie, you are still so thoughtful.

425
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,000
Then, Zheng,

426
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:28,400
take the supplies and set off immediately.

427
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,480
If there is any news,

428
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,880
report back immediately.

429
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,440
I

430
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,350
obey.

431
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:33,200
Wait.

432
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,000
The situation in Huangpi Village

433
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,750
may be more complex than we imagined.

434
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:37,830
You must be careful

435
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,000
and protect yourself and Xiao Chi.

436
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:40,880
I understand.

437
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,830
Please rest assured,

438
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,630
Your Majesty and Your Highness.

439
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,810
I will take my leave.

440
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:53,000
Xie, you are the backbone of Jinglan.

441
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:55,400
Then give me the throne.

442
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:57,270
You can have it.

443
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:59,030
Anyway, you won't treat me badly.

444
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:01,070
I'd rather be an idle prince.

445
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,460
You little clever one.

446
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:04,240
The people of Jinglan

447
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,350
and the glory of the Liu family,

448
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:07,240
now rest on your shoulders.

449
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:09,050
Even if you want to be idle,

450
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:09,960
I,

451
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:10,820
the officials,

452
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:12,270
and our late father

453
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:13,480
will not agree.

454
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:18,160
You are carrying the whole country
of Jinglan on your shoulders.

455
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,220
Do you understand?

456
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:20,550
I understand.

457
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:43,200
Cuizhi.

458
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,590
Cuizhi.

459
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:45,550
What's wrong?

460
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,030
Physician Han,

461
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:48,070
Physician Han, come quickly.

462
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,670
My sister is vomiting blood.

463
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:51,830
Help her up first.

464
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:52,690
Physician Han.

465
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:53,510
Come.

466
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:57,110
Sit down.

467
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,480
Go get some ginseng slices.

468
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:00,070
Okay.

469
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:11,920
How could there be signs of poisoning?

470
00:20:16,830 --> 00:20:17,400
Come on.

471
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,600
Keep this in your mouth.

472
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,790
How is my sister?

473
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,880
She's fine for now.

474
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:51,730
Thank you, Physician Han.

475
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,950
We can never repay your great kindness.

476
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:57,160
You stay here and take care of her.

477
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:57,880
Okay.

478
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,200
Why won't you let me out?

479
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,000
We are short of
medicinal herbs in the village.

480
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,750
I need to go out to buy medicinal herbs.

481
00:21:11,750 --> 00:21:12,550
Without an order,

482
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,070
no one is allowed in or out.

483
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:14,000
Physician Chen.

484
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:16,030
What happened?

485
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:17,760
General Xiao.

486
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,400
The guards suddenly
stopped me from leaving today,

487
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,270
saying the Death Plague

488
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:24,530
in Huangpi Village is severe
and no one is allowed in or out.

489
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,000
We don't have enough medicine now.

490
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,270
Physician Chen needs
to go out to gather medicinal herbs.

491
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:28,070
Besides,

492
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:30,030
the situation in the village has improved.

493
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:31,560
Who says it's that serious?

494
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,200
This is an order from above.

495
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:35,000
General Xiao, please
don't make it difficult for us.

496
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:36,640
I know you're following orders,

497
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,030
but we must get the medicine.

498
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:38,830
Lord Xiao.

499
00:21:39,110 --> 00:21:41,270
We are acting on Lord Zhang's orders.

500
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:44,030
Without an order,
no one is allowed in or out.

501
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,510
Lord Zhang's orders?

502
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:48,960
But this is a matter
of life and death for the villagers.

503
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:51,160
Sorry, military orders must be obeyed.

504
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,880
Fine. In that case,

505
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,530
pardon me for being rough.

506
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:02,880
Stop!

507
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,750
Zheng?

508
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:10,590
Lord Fei.

509
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:12,750
We are ordered by Lord Zhang
to stand guard here.

510
00:22:12,750 --> 00:22:15,030
Without an order,
no one is allowed to leave the village.

511
00:22:15,030 --> 00:22:15,790
I am here

512
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,550
by imperial decree.

513
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:18,440
What?

514
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:21,030
Does His Majesty

515
00:22:21,030 --> 00:22:22,830
have to listen to Lord Zhang now?

516
00:22:23,270 --> 00:22:24,200
I wouldn't dare.

517
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:27,400
Chi,

518
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:29,250
you've worked hard lately.

519
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:31,440
How is the situation in the village now?

520
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:34,000
The situation in the village
is much better now.

521
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,510
Then these supplies and medicines...

522
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:36,440
Put them inside.

523
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:37,550
Thank you, Zheng.

524
00:22:38,350 --> 00:22:39,550
Listen up, everyone.

525
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:42,070
Unload the supplies
and medicines from the carts

526
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,070
and transport them into the village.

527
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,030
Yes, Sir.

528
00:22:45,590 --> 00:22:46,400
Let's go.

529
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:02,690
Physician Han.

530
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,480
Lord Fei.

531
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:10,200
Is Cuizhi's condition

532
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:11,640
looking bad?

533
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,240
Cuizhi's pulse

534
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:16,810
shows signs of poisoning.

535
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,200
Poisoning?

536
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,420
How could this happen?

537
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,440
Then is there

538
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:25,050
any cure for the poison?

539
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,640
There is a way,

540
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,200
but the medicine is very strong.

541
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,800
I have never tried it before.

542
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:32,490
Physician Han, do you want

543
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:34,520
to test the medicine on people?

544
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:38,070
I need to confirm first

545
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:40,270
if a healthy person
will be okay after taking this medicine.

546
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:41,240
If they are fine,

547
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:43,040
then I'll use it on the patients.

548
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:44,880
Time is running out.

549
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,880
I'll go prepare the medicine first.

550
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,000
Xiao Chi,

551
00:23:53,590 --> 00:23:54,880
I'll return to the capital right now

552
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,410
and find a death row inmate.

553
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,640
I'm warning you,

554
00:23:58,480 --> 00:23:59,960
don't do anything stupid.

555
00:24:00,590 --> 00:24:02,030
Don't worry, Zheng.

556
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,110
I'll be back as soon as possible.

557
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:04,550
Okay.

558
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,000
Physician Han.

559
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,260
The medicine is ready.

560
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:17,750
Why don't you test it on my sister?

561
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:18,960
If anything happens,

562
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:20,200
I won't blame anyone.

563
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,440
Don't worry.

564
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,080
This is the minimum dose.

565
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:24,270
I need to find

566
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:27,070
the right dosage for
both the healthy and the sick.

567
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,000
Are you going to test it on yourself?

568
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,030
Why are you here?

569
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:31,430
Get out of here right now.

570
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,640
If you're going to test the medicine,

571
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:33,160
I...

572
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,160
I didn't drink it.

573
00:24:35,350 --> 00:24:37,350
The whole village is
waiting for me to save them.

574
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:39,080
I won't gamble with my own body.

575
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,680
Really?

576
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,070
Look.

577
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:44,550
If I really drank it,

578
00:24:44,550 --> 00:24:46,030
how could I be completely fine?

579
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:46,640
But...

580
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,550
Alright.

581
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,360
Wait for my good news.

582
00:24:58,640 --> 00:25:00,240
Jin Xi, turn around.

583
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,090
You have a good eye.

584
00:25:04,550 --> 00:25:06,030
We chose it together.

585
00:25:19,550 --> 00:25:21,070
Is Lord Fei back?

586
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,000
Not yet.

587
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,480
Is the stuff ready?

588
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:25,960
Mhm.

589
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:28,730
Give it to me.

590
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,440
What is this?

591
00:25:32,880 --> 00:25:35,000
Blood from my sister's fingertip.

592
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,160
What is it for?

593
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:38,110
Physician Han...

594
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:38,880
Cuimiao.

595
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,200
Physician Han wants
to use my sister's blood

596
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,000
to get infected,

597
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,830
and then continue testing the medicine.

598
00:25:43,830 --> 00:25:44,640
I'm leaving.

599
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:46,680
Do you have a death wish?

600
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:51,160
If I can use my life

601
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:53,200
to save the whole Huangpi Village,

602
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:54,680
it's worth it.

603
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:59,480
If anyone should do it, it should be me.

604
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,000
Xiao Chi!

605
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,310
My body

606
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:06,070
is already sick anyway.

607
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,110
This way, you can find the cure faster.

608
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:08,640
Xiao Chi, spit the blood out!

609
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,590
Spit it out right now!

610
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:10,510
Calm down.

611
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:11,400
Listen to me.

612
00:26:11,790 --> 00:26:12,550
It has to be me

613
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,270
who tests the medicine.

614
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:15,310
But your body

615
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:17,030
can't take any more torture.

616
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,680
My body is already like this.

617
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,000
It makes no difference
whether I test it or not.

618
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,260
But you're different.

619
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,340
You are everyone's only hope now.

620
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,070
And,

621
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:29,320
I don't want anything
to happen to you either.

622
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:41,240
Then stay here tonight.

623
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,460
Don't go anywhere.

624
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:43,350
Okay.

625
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:45,830
Lie down first.

626
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:49,080
Is there a reaction already?

627
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,960
It's fine.

628
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:52,750
I just drank too fast.

629
00:26:52,750 --> 00:26:54,080
Just pour me a pot of tea.

630
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:55,880
Go sit down first.

631
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,840
I'll go pour you some tea.

632
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,010
Cuimiao.

633
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:11,830
Yes.

634
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:13,590
Go bring General Xiao some tea.

635
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,480
Okay.

636
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:29,130
Physician Han.

637
00:27:29,310 --> 00:27:30,030
Physician Han.

638
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:30,590
Physician Han!

639
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:32,590
General Xiao threw up a lot of blood!

640
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,790
Go find Physician Chen.

641
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:34,400
Okay.

642
00:27:39,830 --> 00:27:40,640
I'm fine.

643
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,720
Physician Han,

644
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:57,200
General Xiao threw up so much black blood.

645
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,440
Will he die?

646
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,880
Don't talk nonsense, little girl.

647
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,200
The general won't die.

648
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,440
Physician Han,

649
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:04,480
how is it?

650
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,640
General Xiao has a high fever now.

651
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,370
He is likely already infected.

652
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:14,090
I want to try that prescription on him.

653
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,880
But if we use the medicine rashly

654
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,640
and something happens here,

655
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:21,570
I'm afraid we won't be able
to bear the consequences.

656
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:22,790
It's fine.

657
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,410
I administered

658
00:28:24,550 --> 00:28:26,070
the poison to myself.

659
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,050
Is the medicine ready?

660
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:30,640
Bring it over.

661
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:35,390
-Go get the medicine.
-Okay.

662
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:41,680
I'm fine.

663
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:06,830
General Xiao.

664
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:10,160
I'm fine.

665
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,790
How is that possible?

666
00:29:33,640 --> 00:29:36,000
I only used half the dosage.

667
00:29:39,790 --> 00:29:41,250
General Xiao's condition

668
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,640
is not looking good.

669
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,640
Plus he himself

670
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,790
is naturally weak.

671
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:48,440
If he can't make it through tonight,

672
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:50,350
our lives are in danger.

673
00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:53,790
Actually, there is another way.

674
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:54,830
Then treat him quickly.

675
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,440
H-His condition can't wait.

676
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,840
It's just that this acupuncture method...

677
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:00,070
Xiao Chi.

678
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,200
Xiao Chi.

679
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:03,750
Xiao Chi.

680
00:30:07,270 --> 00:30:08,270
I'm fine.

681
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:09,750
I'm fine.

682
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,480
There's no time to lose.

683
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:13,640
Physician Chen,
please undress General Xiao.
